Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

Class GameModel

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.GameModel
public class GameModel extends Object
This class contains the state of the game items. There is no information about players' turns and connections/disconnections, as they are handled in the controller package.

      Parameters:
      decks - decks to be used during game phase
      playerTokens - tokens playing
      tokenToStarterCard - map from token to the StarterCard card chosen
      tokenToCardSide - map from token to the CardSide chosen
      tokenToObjectiveCard - map from token to the ObjectiveCard card chosen
      commonObjectives - common objectives drawn
      observers - list of observers
      lastEventId - integer used to uniquely identify events
